item.description:
Hi Gang, join us for an evening of fun, we will be exploring Dover bars and nightclubs, so come out and  join us. We will be having a light dinner and then walking the streets and checking out the local nightspots.

So if you have nothing to do and would like some company come out and have fun meeting new people and seeing a new town!

If  you have any questions or just trying to locate me, call me at: 603-312-6735. See you there! Peter
